{"type":"text","timestamp":1783438596276,"sessionID":"ses_0c2c700d9ffeA6s9UJ7ileTTQO","part":{"id":"prt_f3d39513a001D6NhGdHG52cxiJ","messageID":"msg_f3d394953001pHjUvMmhNceqDQ","sessionID":"ses_0c2c700d9ffeA6s9UJ7ileTTQO","type":"text","text":"```json\n{\n  \"anomaly_ids\": [],\n  \"answer\": \"当前应使用《XX证券费用报销管理办法(2025修订版)》（现行有效版本）所规定的金额。2025修订版正文不再列示具体审批金额，统一按《XX证券授权管理办法》附件二的金额档位执行：单笔金额＜3000元由部门经理审批，3000元（含）~10000元由部门经理+财务复核，10000元（含）~50000元由部门总经理审批，50000元（含）~200000元由分管副总审批，≥200000元由总经理办公会审批。原《XX证券费用报销管理办法(2022版)》已于2025年1月1日起废止，其载明的8000元/30000元等审批金额不得作为现行依据。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"02_expense_reimbursement_2022_deprecated.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第一条\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"02_expense_reimbursement_2022_deprecated.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第四条\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第十四条\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第五条\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第二条\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"附件二\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```","time":{"start":1783438594362,"end":1783438596253}}}
